==Chinese==
[[Category:Chinese language]]
===Verb===
'''解決''' (traditional); '''<font lang="zh">[[解]][[决]]</font>''' (simplified) (Pinyin: jiějué)
# to [[resolve]] a problem

==Japanese==
[[Category:Japanese language|にほんこ]]
===Etymology===
[[解]] (かい, kai), ''solution'' + [[決]] (けつ, ketsu), ''decisive''

===Noun===
'''解決''' (かいけつ, kaiketsu)

# a [[conclusion]] to a problem

===Verb===
'''解決する''' (かいけつする, kaiketsu suru)

# to [[resolve]] a problem
#: ''問題は解決した。''
#: ''もんだいはかいけつした。''
#: ''mondai wa kaiketsu shita''
#: ''The problem was resolved.''

[[zh:解決]]